[normal]INTRODUCTION
[normal]This written evidence is given in response to an invitation to comment on Part P schemes. 
[normal]It is given in 3 sections, 
[normal]SUMMARY OF 
[normal]RECOMMENDATIONS, OBSERVATIONS and 
[normal]BIBLIOGRAPHY
